DESCRIPTION:

The legendary Philips edition - The Complete Compact Mozart Edition is reissued in time for the 2006 anniversary. Originally released in 2001, this 180-CD collection contains Mozart&#039;s complete oeuvre and has proven to be the most successful edition in the history of the recording industry. The massive undertaking of recording the 45 volumes was preceded by years of preparation and included many recordings of pieces that had never previously seen the light of day! The hard labour, love and devotion that had been put into this brave and ambitious project would never have been possible without the inspiration that the world&#039;s most beloved composer had given to so many of the people involved.
